<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:14:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国高级议员将再次就中国棉花问题致信Shein</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/senior-uk-lawmaker-write-shein-again-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席计划第二次写信给Shein，再次询问这家在线快时尚零售商是否将含有棉花的产品从中国新疆地区运往英国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/senior-uk-lawmaker-write-shein-again-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将人工智能、生物技术和廉价能源作为推动全球竞争力的目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-pushes-massive-pause-eu-red-tape-amid-us-pressure-2025-01-24/</link><description>路透社看到的欧盟委员会文件草案显示，人工智能、生物技术和负担得起的清洁能源将成为欧盟努力提高欧盟全球竞争力并确保与美国和中国保持同步的重点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-pushes-massive-pause-eu-red-tape-amid-us-pressure-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Telia 出售马歇尔集团股份，中国洪山公司以 11.5 亿美元收购马歇尔集团股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-hongshan-buys-majority-stake-marshall-group-115-bln-deal-2025-01-24/</link><description>HongShan Capital Group 周五表示，已达成协议，收购 Marshall Group 的多数股权，该交易对这家音频设备制造商的估值为 11 亿欧元（11.5 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-hongshan-buys-majority-stake-marshall-group-115-bln-deal-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Shein告诉英国立法者，不允许在美国销售的产品中使用中国棉花</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</link><description>在线快时尚零售商 Shein 周五表示，要求其合同制造商只能从经批准的地区（不包括中国）采购棉花，用于在其最大市场美国销售产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商江淮汽车预计2024年净亏损，受大众合资企业打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-jac-expects-2024-net-loss-hit-by-vw-venture-2025-01-24/</link><description>安徽江淮汽车集团（JAC）周五表示，预计 2024 年业绩将出现亏损，理由是其与大众的合资企业业绩疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-jac-expects-2024-net-loss-hit-by-vw-venture-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾漫画向儿童讲述南海之战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-comic-book-takes-battle-south-china-sea-children-2025-01-24/</link><description>菲律宾周五推出了一本漫画书，以对抗所谓的有关有争议的南中国海海洋权利的歪曲叙述，此举招致了中国的批评。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:11:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-comic-book-takes-battle-south-china-sea-children-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：随着日本央行加息，美元下跌，欧元区增长，人民币松了口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:06:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>文本显示美国立法者寻求对香港进行人权制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</link><description>据路透社看到的法案文本，美国共和党和民主党议员将于周五提出一项法案，要求特朗普政府审查是否应因侵犯人权而对香港官员进行制裁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:05:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：律师称，赌博大亨因称自己为中国从事间谍活动而在泰国监狱中受到虐待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</link><description>一名被监禁的赌博大亨的律师告诉国际刑警组织，他们担心他的生命安全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>泰国和中国将设立打击诈骗电话网络协调中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</link><description>泰国和中国将共同努力，打击泰国、缅甸和柬埔寨边境沿线快速增长的非法呼叫中心网络，这些呼叫中心的工作人员通常是被贩运的工人，旨在通过电话和网络诈骗来诈骗人们。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>POLL 中国一月制造业活动连续第四个月扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/poll-china-jan-manufacturing-activity-seen-expanding-fourth-month-2025-01-24/</link><description>1月份中国工厂活动可能连续第四个月扩张，突显了世界第二大经济体的供给侧实力，美国关税上调可能进一步削弱国内需求并加剧通货紧缩压力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/poll-china-jan-manufacturing-activity-seen-expanding-fourth-month-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国2024年财政收入增速萎缩非税收入跃升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-2024-fiscal-revenue-grows-13-down-64-year-earlier-2025-01-24/</link><description>财政部周五公布的数据显示，由于房地产市场持续低迷和内需放缓给经济带来压力，2024年中国财政收入同比增长1.3%，较2023年6.4%的增幅大幅放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:16:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-2024-fiscal-revenue-grows-13-down-64-year-earlier-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫在特朗普发表评论后表示，普京希望重启核武器削减谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-wants-restart-nuclear-arms-cuts-talks-kremlin-says-after-trump-comment-2025-01-24/</link><description>克里姆林宫周五在回应美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的评论时表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已明确表示，他希望尽快重启核武器削减谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 09:52:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-wants-restart-nuclear-arms-cuts-talks-kremlin-says-after-trump-comment-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构表示，特斯拉将为超过 120 万辆进口和中国制造的汽车修复软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-over-12-million-imported-china-made-cars-says-regulator-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国市场监管机构称，特斯拉将对部分进口Model S和X以及国产Model 3和Y汽车的安全隐患进行软件修复，总计超过120万辆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-over-12-million-imported-china-made-cars-says-regulator-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>共同社称，中国男子因刺死日本男孩而被判处死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</link><description>日本共同社周五援引日本驻华大使金杉健二的话报道称，中国南部城市深圳一男子因刺伤一名日本男孩而被中国法院判处死刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>